After installing it, each biome in the MCPE game will become better. The spawn of hills, trees, villages and other elements will change and become cooler! The player will have a greater chance of stumbling into hidden, atmospheric villages. And biome landscapes will bewitch the views. In addition, this addon contains shaders that will change the lighting and elaboration of the game world. If you look at the screenshot of Hell, you will understand how much the lighting will change.

Map.name: Avengers: Infinity War Special (Burn It) [Minigame]

The map serves three purposes; first, it is a burn it map and every Avengers statue is hollow and your objective is to survive for as long as possible as lava comes down on the players inside. The map also has several Easter eggs from all of the MCU movies as well as some other handful bits and pieces of information in regards to the movies.

Yet it didn't stay the headquarters for the Avengers for long - after the battle with Ultron Tony Stark started to build the new Avengers Facility with Stark Industries taking over the use of the tower again.
